quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  110,1,"When the help comes from Allah, and victory (is granted),",footnotes:182876:1
  110,2,"and you see people entering Allah's religion in multitudes,",footnotes:182877:1
  110,3,"then extol the praise of your Lord and pray to Him for forgiveness. For He indeed is ever disposed to accept repentance.",footnotes:182878:1|182879:2
